## 6. on-session-start.sh Task ID Propagation

**File:** `/Users/frikk.jarl/Documents/GitHub/doey/.claude/hooks/on-session-start.sh`
**Lines:** 131, 186-188

When a worker starts in a team with TASK_ID, on-session-start.sh reads it from the team env and exports it:
```bash
_team_task_id=$(_read_team_key "${RUNTIME_DIR}/team_${TEAM_WINDOW}.env" TASK_ID)
# ...
if [ -n "${_team_task_id:-}" ]; then
  echo "export DOEY_TASK_ID=\"${_team_task_id}\"" >> "$CLAUDE_ENV_FILE"
fi
```

**Verdict: CORRECT** — workers inherit the task ID from their team env.

